Red Mountain Capital Partners LLC











































































Active Owners.
Proactive Partners.










Our Mission


We are active, long-term investors in small cap public companies, focusing on the consumer and financial services sectors. With diligence and engagement comparable to that of private equity, we seek to work alongside companies to drive shareholder value.







Strategy

We seek to buy fundamentally sound businesses that are trading at attractive valuations with opportunities to drive shareholder value through enhanced operations, better capital allocation, stronger management and improved governance.








About




Founded in 2005, Red Mountain is an investment firm based in Los Angeles that pursues an active ownership strategy with respect to small cap public consumer and financial services companies through a concentrated closed-end fund.  







Signatory of UNPRI

Red Mountain is a signatory of the United Nations Principles for Responsible Investment (UNPRI).








