Red Mountain Capital Partners LLC Key Developments

Investor Calls For Deckers Outdoor To Put Itself Up For Sale
Mar 27 17
Deckers Outdoor Corporation (NYSE:DECK) is up about 2% in early after-hours trade after Red Mountain Capital Partners LLC, which owns about 3.3% of Deckers stock, said it has sent a letter to the company requesting it put itself up for sale.


Red Mountain Urges iRobot To Explore Strategic Alternatives Including Sale
Dec 1 15
In a letter to Colin Angle, the Chairman and Chief Executive Office of iRobot Corporation (NasdaqGS:IRBT), Red Mountain Capital Partners LLC suggested iRobot to explore strategic alternatives for the defense and security business, discontinue the remote presence business, focus on the high- growth Home Robots business and the consumer end-market, allocate capital with discipline and an intense focus on risk-adjusted returns and address significant lapses in corporate governance. In addition, Red Mountain said that the Board should consider all other paths to maximize shareholder value, including a sale of iRobot as an alternative to the implementation of the proposed value enhancement plan.


